<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy — Donna</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --ink: #1a1a1a;
      --muted: #6b6b6b;
      --rule: #e0ddd8;
      --bg: #f9f7f4;
      --accent: #2c4a3e;
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .wordmark {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .wordmark span {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-left: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    nav {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    nav a {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    nav a:hover, nav a.active { color: var(--accent); }

    main {
      padding: 4rem 0 6rem;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 2.75rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .meta {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin: 2.5rem 0 0.875rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 0.975rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #3a3a3a;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    ul {
      margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 1.25rem;
    }

    li {
      font-size: 0.975rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #3a3a3a;
      margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
    }

    .contact-block {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--rule);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .contact-block p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }

    footer p {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="wordmark">Donna <span>Executive Assistant</span></div>
      <nav>
        <a href="privacy.html" class="active">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="terms.html">Terms &amp; Conditions</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="meta">Effective Date: April 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Last Updated: April 2026</p>

      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>This Privacy Policy applies to SMS and MMS communications sent by Donna, the personal AI executive assistant of Nick Whittington. It describes how personal information is collected, used, and protected in connection with these communications.</p>

      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>Donna is a personal AI executive assistant operating on behalf of Nick Whittington. Messages sent from this service originate from Donna acting as Nick's representative in personal and professional matters.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>In connection with SMS/MMS communications, we may collect or use:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your phone number, for the purpose of sending and receiving messages</li>
        <li>The content of messages exchanged</li>
        <li>Your name and contact information, as provided by Nick Whittington</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>Your information is used solely to facilitate relevant communications on Nick Whittington's behalf, including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Appointment reminders and scheduling confirmations</li>
        <li>Project coordination and status updates</li>
        <li>Household and personal logistics</li>
        <li>Follow-ups related to existing professional or personal relationships</li>
      </ul>

      <hr class="divider">

      <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing or any unrelated purpose. Your contact information is used exclusively for communications initiated on behalf of Nick Whittington.</p>

      <h2>Message Frequency</h2>
      <p>Message frequency varies based on the nature of your relationship with Nick Whittington and active projects or appointments. There is no fixed schedule for communications.</p>

      <h2>Opting Out</h2>
      <p>You may opt out of receiving messages at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong> to any message. After opting out, you will no longer receive SMS or MMS communications from this service. To request assistance, reply <strong>HELP</strong>.</p>

      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>We take reasonable precautions to protect your personal information. Message content is not stored beyond what is necessary to fulfill the purpose of the communication.</p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>Nick Whittington reserves the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Continued receipt of messages following any update constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.</p>

      <div class="contact-block">
        <p>Questions about this policy? Contact Nick Whittington directly via your existing communication channel.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Nick Whittington. Donna is a personal AI executive assistant.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
